# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Docker Ignore — Root Level
# Exclude unnecessary files from Docker build context
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Node modules (will be installed in container)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build

# Environment files (use docker-compose environment instead)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Git
.git
.gitignore
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Documentation
*.md
!README.md

# IDE
.vscode
.idea
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Logs
**/logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Database files (SQLite - not used in Docker)
**/dev.db
**/dev.db-journal
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal

# Uploads (will be in volume)
**/uploads

# Test files
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# Coverage
**/coverage

# Temporary files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/.cache

# Build artifacts
**/.next/cache
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Scripts (not needed in container)
*.bat
*.sh
!docker-entrypoint.sh
!entrypoint.sh

# Docker files (don't copy into container)
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore
